Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Moving to unicode for literal values
- Adding a synchronous/asynchronous mode on graphs
- Adding adapters to get some basic resources from capsule documents
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- Statement reification attempt did not take care of the graph internal
  representation
- Querying a Redland graph with a unicode query string was not possible.
- The method to delete all relations now recreates the storage, instead
  of deleting all the relations.
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Redland graphs: database name with mysql backend can be specified in ZMI.
- Redland graphs: graph clearing was failing using a MySQL backend.
